@startuml
title UC08 - Enviar Cupom por E-mail (Aluno e Empresa)

actor Aluno as A
boundary "Perfil do Aluno\nNext.js" as Front
control "ResgateVantagemController\nMicronaut" as Ctrl
queue "RabbitMQ\nFila: cupons.email" as Rabbit
control "EmailConsumer" as Consumer
control "EmailService" as EmailService
actor "Sistema de E-mail" as Mail

A -> Front: Resgata vantagem
Front -> Ctrl: POST /resgates
Ctrl -> Ctrl: Salva resgate e gera cupom
Ctrl -> Rabbit: Publica evento\nCupomResgatadoEvent
Ctrl --> Front: 201 Created\nResgateResponse
Front --> A: Toast de sucesso

Rabbit -> Consumer: Entrega mensagem
Consumer -> EmailService: enviarCupomAluno(resgate)
EmailService -> Mail: Envia e-mail para aluno
Mail --> EmailService: Confirma envio
Consumer -> EmailService: enviarCupomEmpresa(resgate)
EmailService -> Mail: Envia e-mail para empresa
Mail --> EmailService: Confirma envio
Consumer -> Rabbit: ACK mensagem

@enduml
